body:
Fixes the following scenario which resulted in a hang.
Begin work;
insert into table t  values( 1);
drop table t;
commit work;

In this scenario, as part of commit, the drop table t gets hadmin:disabled in prepare phase followed by hadmin delete in commit phase. However, because there was a insert to table, commit phase encounters the disabled table. Fix is to detect this exception in the commit thread and validate against the drop table list maintained in TmDDL log.
